data.description: Own this spacious 3 bedroom 2 bath, one story home with 2159 sq ft of living space on a 10,000 sq ft lot, and a nearby Golf Course! Great for 1st time home buyers or investors. Kitchen & bathroom w/tile & linoleum flooring. Selling As Is. Great location, local shopping & restaurants, & quick access to freeway. Within distance to Fairfield Amtrak Station, Travis Air Force Base,  parks, and schools. Fairfield Train transportation will take you to the Bay Area or to Sacramento. Local wineries in Fairfield and also in the Napa Valley. Don't miss this wonderful opportunity to own this home. Please come see this in person before it's too late!
